OL,3,CCeltic boss urged to apologise over
OL,4,C'good girl' comment
OL,6,FA women's group has described Celtic
OL,7,Fmanager Brendan Rodgers' comments to a
OL,8,Ffemale journalist as "demeaning" and
OL,9,Fwarned they could encourage similar
OL,10,Fbehaviour from football fans.
OL,12,FDuring a BBC Sportsound radio
OL,13,Finterview following Sunday's 3-1 win
OL,14,Fagainst Motherwell, Mr Rodgers was
OL,15,Fheard saying "good girl" following a
OL,16,Fline of questioning from the
OL,17,Fbroadcaster's reporter Jane Lewis.
