OL,3,CCeltic boss urged to apologise over
OL,4,C'good girl' comment
OL,6,FThe Scottish Feminist Network and For
OL,7,FWomen Scotland have urged Mr Rodgers
OL,8,Fto explain the comment, which has been
OL,9,Flabelled as "casual sexism".
OL,11,FOn the Sunday programme, Ms Lewis
OL,12,Fasked the Celtic boss to elaborate on
OL,13,Fthe Cinch Premiership title race after
OL,14,Fhe said: "The story has already been
OL,15,Fwritten about this group. But we will
OL,16,Fwrite our own story."
OL,18,FShe said: "Can you give us a bit more
OL,19,F` you don't want to give us a bit more
OL,20,Finsight into that and what you mean?"
