OL,3,CCeltic boss urged to apologise over
OL,4,C'good girl' comment
OL,6,FHe replied: "No, no, you know exactly
OL,7,Fwhat I mean", with the journalist
OL,8,Freplying: "I'm actually not sure
OL,9,Fexactly what you mean."
OL,11,FHe then appeared to wrap up the
OL,12,Finterview by saying: "Done, good girl,
OL,13,Fwell done."
OL,15,FMs Lewis has not commented on the
OL,16,Fremarks and the BBC and Celtic FC have
OL,17,Fbeen approached for a response.
