OL,4,C'good girl' comment
OL,6,FA spokeswoman for the Scottish
OL,7,FFeminist Network said: "Rodgers'
OL,8,Fthrowaway comment encourages other
OL,9,Ffootball fans to behave in a similar
OL,10,Fway..
OL,12,F"It has to stop.
OL,14,F"Jane Lewis was just doing her job,
OL,15,Ftrying to extract an explanation from
OL,16,FBrendan Rodgers on his cryptic comment.
