OL,3,CCeltic boss urged to apologise over
OL,4,C'good girl' comment
OL,6,F"That the go-to attitude of a manager
OL,7,Fof a winning team was condescension is
OL,8,Fquite illuminating but really very
OL,9,Fdepressing in 2024. We thought
OL,10,Fdinosaurs were extinct."
OL,12,FA spokeswoman at For Women Scotland
OL,13,Fsaid: "It's depressing that casual
OL,14,Fsexism is still embedded in sport.
OL,16,F"Women's achievements are underrated
OL,17,Fand dismissed, and their professional
OL,18,Fstatus undermined. Rodgers owes the
OL,19,Freporter an apology."
